        <div class=3D"section collapsed" id=3D"section-pre-header-section">=
<div class=3D"section-container"><p>The <strong>Chinese remainder theorem</=
strong> is a theorem which gives a unique solution to simultaneous linear c=
ongruences with coprime moduli. In its basic form, the Chinese remainder th=
eorem will determine a number \(p\) that, when divided by some given diviso=
rs, leaves given remainders. </p>

</div>
</div>

